description:
VTK is an open-source, freely available software system for 3D computer graphics, image processing, and visualization.
      This package statically link your VTK code with pre-built libraries, which enables you to build a standalone application.
      Toolset: MSVC 14.1 (Visual Studio 2017)
      Platform: x64
      Configuration: Release
